data.description: PRISTINE 4 bedroom 3 bath ranch over partially finished basement located in the Waynesville School District! The immaculate lawn and covered front porch will greet you as you enter the home. The living room features a vaulted ceiling and is carpeted for comfort. The kitchen and dining area feature ample cabinet and counter space with updated appliances, ceramic tile flooring, two pantries and access to the 10x20 deck and fenced in rear yard and patio! The Owner's Suite is generous with a custom ceiling design, large walk in closet and a luxury bath with jetted tub, dual vanity, fully tiled shower and a private water closet. There are 2 additional bedrooms on the other side of the home for added privacy that share a full bath in the hall! The lower level offers a gigantic family room, 4th bedroom, 3rd full bath, storage room and a John Deere room that's perfect for storing all of your yard equipment, tools and toys! This home has everything you need for your growing family! Call today!
